  <section class="webtools-container">

    <h1>Webtools description</h1>
    <p>
      Webtools is a framework to ease building static website.
      It includes
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li> preprocessor capabilities, include of common parts of the website,</li>
      <li> minification of files, </li>
      <li> image optimization, </li>
      <li>and automatic validation of the built website.</li>
    </ul>


    <h2> Installation </h2>
    <p>
      Install the sources: the framework, as well as the test website (this one!)
      <code>
        git clone https://github.com/pascal-brand38/webtools.git
      </code>
    </p>

    <p>
      Install dependencies:
      <code>
        npm install
      </code>
    </p>

